---
title: MyAIStorybook FYP-2 — State Diagram: Story Lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE : System ready

    IDLE --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : User submits prompt

    PROMPT_RECEIVED --> STT_PROCESSING : [voice input selected]
    STT_PROCESSING --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : Whisper transcribes audio

    PROMPT_RECEIVED --> VALIDATING : Prompt submitted to backend

    VALIDATING --> IDLE : [Invalid/Nonsense]\nError returned to user
    VALIDATING --> GENERATING_TEXT : [Valid prompt]

    GENERATING_TEXT --> REVIEWING : Writer Agent completes story draft

    REVIEWING --> GENERATING_TEXT : [Coherence failed]\nRetry max 2x
    REVIEWING --> EDITING : [Story approved by Reviewer]

    EDITING --> EXPORTING_PDF : Editor finalizes metadata

    EXPORTING_PDF --> IMAGE_GENERATION : [generate_images=true]\nOllama paused

    state IMAGE_GENERATION {
        [*] --> SCENE_1
        SCENE_1 --> SCENE_2 : txt2img + img2img done
        SCENE_2 --> SCENE_3 : txt2img + img2img done
        SCENE_3 --> [*] : All scenes complete
    }

    IMAGE_GENERATION --> COMPLETED : Images saved\nOllama resumed
    EXPORTING_PDF --> COMPLETED : [generate_images=false]\nText-only story

    COMPLETED --> EVALUATING : EvaluationAgent triggered\n(async background)
    EVALUATING --> COMPLETED : Metrics saved to JSON

    COMPLETED --> NARRATING : User clicks Play
    NARRATING --> NARRATING : Change page / switch voice
    NARRATING --> COMPLETED : User stops playback

    COMPLETED --> CHATTING : User opens Character Chat
    CHATTING --> CHATTING : Multi-turn conversation
    CHATTING --> COMPLETED : Chat closed

    COMPLETED --> WORKSHOP : User starts Idea Workshop
    WORKSHOP --> WORKSHOP : Requirements collection
    WORKSHOP --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : Requirements complete

    COMPLETED --> [*] : Session ends

    GENERATING_TEXT --> ERROR : LLM unavailable
    STT_PROCESSING --> ERROR : Whisper model error
    IMAGE_GENERATION --> COMPLETED : Image fails - graceful degradation
    ERROR --> IDLE : User retries
